====================
Address for Thailand
====================

If country is selected as Thailand, new fields will show up.

* Province (Chanwat)
* District (Amphoe)
* Township (Tambon)

Choosing Township will realize Province, District, and Zip Code

Usage
=====

The new Thailand address fields are available in Customer / Supplier windows.

.. image:: https://odoo-community.org/website/image/ir.attachment/5784_f2813bd/datas
   :alt: Try me on Runbot
   :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/{repo_id}/{branch}

.. repo_id is available in https://github.com/OCA/maintainer-tools/blob/master/tools/repos_with_ids.txt
.. branch is "8.0" for example

<https://github.com/OCA/l10n-thailand/issues>`_. In case of trouble, please

help us smash it by providing detailed and welcomed feedback.
